{"tid":1434282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手機被黑警沒收 telegram group小心有鬼","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:25:34.000Z","uid":303205,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52505b9b71bf24d5fa4078714575e2be64f8f612","tid":1434282,"uid":303205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"有朋友西環食花生 被黑警告非法集結<br />\n佢情急下唔小心將手機開咗鎖 黑警cap低telegram group名<br />\n<br />\n以下telegram group小心鬼/警犬<br />\n- 有2-3個個group名關於721 元朗 or 元朗遊行<br />\n- 有1個係關於救救兒童<br />\n- 有1個係哨兵資訊<br />\n<br />\n朋友知自己蠢 但被黑警精神虐待下 開左鎖做左傻事。對唔住各位手足。<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益睇下點小心鬼。定退團重開。"},{"pid":"90f7435f557017f91e9ccad2efee67c4a98dd7d1","tid":1434282,"uid":75582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:25:07.000Z","msg":"講左咁多個月 都可以比狗兇到"},{"pid":"3162a7459fee021e300e5e1f1c3d6fb84bb04910","tid":1434282,"uid":131766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:25:14.000Z","msg":"Tg不嬲都有狗架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eefe4a702d4ccd2fb9f3fb89580d71e8d6c80be","tid":1434282,"uid":233530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:25:32.000Z","msg":"on9無藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過啲group一早已經有鬼啦"},{"pid":"3a5e7c80a90736a64e3a5204b7be9d5df6018097","tid":1434282,"uid":298289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"啊Sir早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}